import Container from "@mui/material/Container";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import Card from "@mui/material/Card";
import MKBox from "components/MKBox";
import MKTypography from "components/MKTypography";
import MKButton from "components/MKButton";

function HomePage() {
  return (
    <>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <MKBox
        minHeight="75vh"
        width="100%"
        sx={{
          backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c')`,
          backgroundSize: "cover",
          backgroundPosition: "center",
          display: "grid",
          placeItems: "center",
        }}
      >
        <Container>
          <Grid container item xs={12} lg={7} justifyContent="center" mx="auto">
            <MKTypography
              variant="h1"
              color="white"
              mt={-6}
              mb={1}
              sx={({ breakpoints, typography: { size } }) => ({
                [breakpoints.down("md")]: {
                  fontSize: size["3xl"],
                },
              })}
            >
              Welcome to Our Platform
            </MKTypography>
            <MKTypography
              variant="body1"
              color="white"
              textAlign="center"
              px={{ xs: 6, lg: 12 }}
              mt={1}
            >
              Discover amazing features and create something beautiful.
            </MKTypography>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </MKBox>

      {/* Features Section */}
      <Container sx={{ mt: 6, mb: 6 }}>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ p: 2, height: "100%" }}>
              <MKBox textAlign="center" py={2}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={2}>
                  Feature 1
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body2" color="text">
                  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                </MKTypography>
                <MKButton color="primary" variant="contained" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                  Learn More
                </MKButton>
              </MKBox>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ p: 2, height: "100%" }}>
              <MKBox textAlign="center" py={2}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={2}>
                  Feature 2
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body2" color="text">
                  Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna.
                </MKTypography>
                <MKButton color="primary" variant="contained" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                  Learn More
                </MKButton>
              </MKBox>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ p: 2, height: "100%" }}>
              <MKBox textAlign="center" py={2}>
                <MKTypography variant="h4" mb={2}>
                  Feature 3
                </MKTypography>
                <MKTypography variant="body2" color="text">
                  Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco.
                </MKTypography>
                <MKButton color="primary" variant="contained" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                  Learn More
                </MKButton>
              </MKBox>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>

      {/* Contact Section */}
      <MKBox bgcolor="grey.100" py={6}>
        <Container>
          <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} md={8} textAlign="center">
              <MKTypography variant="h2" mb={2}>
                Get In Touch
              </MKTypography>
              <MKTypography variant="body1" color="text" mb={4}>
                Have questions? We'd love to hear from you.
              </MKTypography>
              <MKButton color="info" variant="contained" size="large">
                Contact Us
              </MKButton>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </MKBox>
    </>
  );
}

export default HomePage;
